<SYNC Start=1355374><P Class=KRCC>알겠어요
<SYNC Start=1356685><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1402552><P Class=KRCC>맛있네요
<SYNC Start=1403817><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1405447><P Class=KRCC>별말씀을요
<SYNC Start=1406669><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1427899><P Class=KRCC><i>이날 유리코는 수줍음을 감추려고<br>필사적으로 집안일을 처리하고 있었다</i>
<SYNC Start=1433206><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1657535><P Class=KRCC>목욕은?
<SYNC Start=1658548><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1659081><P Class=KRCC>아! 벌써 준비해뒀으니까 먼저 씻으세요
<SYNC Start=1662688><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1664226><P Class=KRCC>그래요
<SYNC Start=1665303><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1669308><P Class=KRCC>함께 들어가지 않을래요
<SYNC Start=1672915><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1673255><P Class=KRCC>예?
<SYNC Start=1674351><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
